    <briefdescription>
<para>Singleton manager that provides access to the current theme. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiThemeManager" kindref="compound">UiThemeManager</ref> is a Handle-based singleton. Theme-level queries (theme ID, theme change notification) are exposed here. Color lookups are accessed through <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiColorManager" kindref="compound">UiColorManager</ref>, not directly through this class.</para>
<para>The <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ThemeLoaderInterface" kindref="compound">ThemeLoaderInterface</ref> instance is created via UiConfigImpl::CreateThemeLoader() during <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiConfig" kindref="compound">UiConfig</ref> initialization. If CreateThemeLoader() returns nullptr, a built-in default loader is used. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
